    "body": "Problem: heap-use-after-free possible when entering Terminal mode if autocommands close the terminal.\r\n\r\nSolution: set the refcount. Skip to the end if we must close the terminal.\r\n\r\n`s->close` is set so we can handle the `close_cb` straight away.\r\nFunnily enough, forgetting to set that causes the test to repro the crash in #38311 on exit. :grin:\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-15T21:38:26Z",
